**/.env
# polish-prompt holds a Turso JWT in a file literally named "env" (no
# dot), which **/.env above does not catch.
config.symlink/polish-prompt/
# himalaya skill is a symlink into the (private) Mail repo and references
# real Gmail addresses + app-password placeholders. Keep it out of dotfiles.
claude.symlink/skills/himalaya
