!claude.symlink/settings.json
!claude.symlink/*.sh
!claude.symlink/go-tools/

# Claude Code local settings (machine-specific)
.claude/settings.local.json

**/logs/
**/codebase-maps/

# Quarto
docs/_book/
docs/.quarto/
docs/_freeze/
docs/site_libs/
docs/*.html
docs/*.tex
docs/*.pdf
docs/**/*_files/
.quarto/
*.zwc
*.zip
